<br>
Here are my questions, regarding CoM.<br>
<br>
1) KC vial can be gotten with a rogue, can CoM?<br>
<br>
2) Would illusion earth elemental work? (ball of golem clay from cazic)<br>
<br>
3) If you arrived invised or invised to undead (friend timed cast as you grav fluxed) could you get close to it (and far enough away from other mobs) that you could turn in bottle?<br>
<br>
Basically I need to know what the mobs are in the vacinity, will they see thru inv or itu, how big their aggro ranges are, and if anyone knows how they react to illusions.<br>
<br>
I want to do this by stealth, there's almost always a way.<br>
<br>
TIA!<br>
<br>
